 development and processing of simulated data may be\napplied to future low-frequency fixed dipole arrays.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 11 Jul 2008 18:56:54 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Mon, 11 Aug 2008 22:19:04 GMT"}],"update_date":"2009-11-13"}
